From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Jack Styles <jackrogers.org@gmail.com>
Date: Sun, 15 Mar 2026 03:30:00 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] Add blocked domains navigation throttle

Integrate StevenBlack/hosts and polarhive/arceo blocklists into Dumb Browser.
Blocks navigation to ~170K domains covering fakenews, gambling, porn, social
media, news, entertainment, and consumerism sites.

The domain list is generated at build time from blocked_domains.txt via a GN
action. A NavigationThrottle intercepts main-frame navigations to blocked
domains and shows a themed blocked page with beautiful nature images and
plum (#412234) branding.
---
 chrome/browser/blocked_domains/BUILD.gn                |  15 +
 chrome/browser/blocked_domains/blocked_domains_navigation_throttle.cc | 245 +
 chrome/browser/blocked_domains/blocked_domains_navigation_throttle.h  |  40 +
 chrome/browser/blocked_domains/blocked_page_images.inc | 2800 +
 chrome/browser/chrome_content_browser_client.cc        |   8 +
 chrome/browser/static_library_browser_deps.gni         |   1 +
 vanadium/blocked_domains/BUILD.gn                      |  20 +
 vanadium/blocked_domains/blocked_domains_data.h        |  18 +
 vanadium/blocked_domains/generate_blocked_domains_data.py | 40 +

